727894f-a.text:
Rockaway Boulevard, west side, north of Farmers Boulevard, showing in the foreground the H. Bedell house of 1860. S. Smith was the owner from 1873 to 1896. J.H. Lambertson was the probable
owner in 1913.
April 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
